1a:["$","tr","5",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Customer Success"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Dedicated CSM per tier"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"AI-assisted, pooled models"}]]}]
1b:["$","tr","6",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Pricing"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Annual contracts, per-seat"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Usage-based, hybrid models"}]]}]
1c:["$","tr","7",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Buyer Expectations"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Demo + trial + sales call"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Self-serve trial, community, peer reviews"}]]}]
1d:["$","p","21",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["The numbers from ICONIQ Growth's May 2026 analysis of the \"Modern GTM Org\" tell a striking story. The firms that have successfully transitioned to the new model are seeing efficiency gains that would have seemed impossible five years ago."]}]
1e:["$","p","23",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["But here's the critical insight for buyers: ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"these efficiency gains come with trade-offs"}],". Understanding those trade-offs helps you pick the right vendor for your specific needs."]}]
1f:["$","h2","25",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"The Three Major Structural Shifts"}]
20:["$","h3","27",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Shift 1: The SDR Role Is Being Compressed or Eliminated"}]
21:["$","p","29",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["The traditional B2B SaaS sales funnel looked like this: Marketing generates leads → SDRs qualify them → AEs close deals → CSMs retain and expand. Each layer added cost, friction, and time to the buyer journey."]}]
22:["$","p","31",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["In 2026's leanest GTM orgs, the SDR tier is being dramatically compressed. Companies like Anthropic (as profiled by SaaStr in May 2026) have rebuilt their sales organizations from scratch, with 54% of new enterprise logos now coming through self-serve channels. No SDR touch required."]}]
23:["$","p","33",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What this means for buyers:"}],""]}]
24:["$","p","34",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Faster initial access"}],": You can trial most SaaS products without talking to a salesperson. The barrier to evaluation has never been lower."]}]
25:["$","p","35",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Less hand-holding"}],": If your team needs extensive onboarding and guided evaluation, you'll need to self-select into the \"high-touch\" track, which may require a minimum spend commitment."]}]
26:["$","p","36",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Price opacity is decreasing"}],": With self-serve first models, list prices are more transparent. But enterprise discounts may be harder to negotiate without a dedicated sales rep advocating for you internally."]}]
27:["$","h3","38",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Shift 2: The Rise of the \"Full-Cycle\" Revenue Role"}]
28:["$","p","40",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Instead of SDR → AE → CSM handoffs, many modern SaaS orgs use a \"full-cycle\" model where one person handles everything from initial conversation through implementation and expansion. This person is typically a domain expert who can speak to product capabilities, use cases, and ROI with genuine depth."]}]
29:["$","p","42",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["This shift is enabled by two factors: AI-powered sales tools handle lead qualification and meeting scheduling, and mature product-led growth (PLG) motions handle the initial education and trial phases."]}]
2a:["$","p","44",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What this means for buyers:"}],""]}]
2b:["$","p","45",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Higher conversation quality"}],": When you do talk to a salesperson, they're more knowledgeable. They can answer technical questions about integrations, APIs, and security — not just pitch features."]}]
2c:["$","p","46",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Smaller teams, less availability"}],": Full-cycle reps are managing more accounts, which means less time for hand-holding. Your initial discovery call may be your only deep-dive session before pricing is presented."]}]
2d:["$","p","47",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Relationship continuity"}],": The person who sells you the software is often the same person who helps you get value from it. This can lead to better alignment between what was promised and what is delivered."]}]
2e:["$","h3","49",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Shift 3: Self-Serve as the Primary Motion, Sales as the Exception"}]
2f:["$","p","51",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["In the 2026 model, self-serve isn't an alternative sales channel — it's the default. Sales-assisted buying is the exception, typically reserved for accounts above a certain ACV threshold ($50K-$100K+ annually)."]}]
30:["$","p","53",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["HubSpot at $3.5B ARR exemplifies this transition. With 248,000+ customers, the vast majority came through self-serve. Even Anthropic, despite its complex AI infrastructure product, reports that over half of new enterprise logos originate from self-serve trials."]}]
31:["$","p","55",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What this means for buyers:"}],""]}]
32:["$","p","56",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Trial before you talk"}],": The expectation is that you will have already used the product before engaging sales. Come prepared with specific questions about your use case."]}]
33:["$","p","57",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Community matters"}],": Self-serve buyers rely heavily on peer reviews, community forums, and knowledge bases. A vendor's community health is now a leading indicator of support quality."]}]
34:["$","p","58",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"The \"enterprise\" tier is a different product"}],": Many vendors now have a genuinely distinct enterprise offering (dedicated infrastructure, custom SLAs, premium support) that requires a sales conversation to access. Don't assume the self-serve tier reflects the full capability."]}]
35:["$","h2","60",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Comparing GTM Models: Which Is Best for Different Buyer Types?"}]
36:["$","p","62",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["To help you navigate vendor selection, I've mapped GTM models to buyer needs:"]}]
37:["$","div","table-70",{"className":"overflow-x-auto mb-6","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm border-collapse","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"className":"bg-[#162440]","children":[["$","th","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#3B82F6] border-b border-[#1E3A5F]","children":"Your Company Size"}],["$","th","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#3B82F6] border-b border-[#1E3A5F]","children":"Best GTM Model"}],["$","th","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#3B82F6] border-b border-[#1E3A5F]","children":"What to Look For"}],["$","th","3",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#3B82F6] border-b border-[#1E3A5F]","children":"What to Avoid"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr","0",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Small (1-50 employees)"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Self-serve first with responsive chat"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Clear pricing, easy trial, active community"}],["$","td","3",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Sales-heavy process for small deals"}]]}],["$","tr","1",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Mid-market (50-500)"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Hybrid: self-serve trial + full-cycle sales"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Fast access to knowledgeable reps, transparent pricing"}],["$","td","3",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Over-automated outreach with generic demos"}]]}],["$","tr","2",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Enterprise (500+)"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"High-touch with dedicated team"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Domain expert reps, custom PoC, flexible contracting"}],["$","td","3",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Pure self-serve with no enterprise pathway"}]]}],["$","tr","3",{"className":"border-b border-[#1E3A5F]/50 hover:bg-[#162440]/50 transition-colors","children":[["$","td","0",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Very Large (5000+)"}],["$","td","1",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Strategic account model"}],["$","td","2",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"C-level relationships, custom integration support, dedicated CS"}],["$","td","3",{"className":"px-4 py-3 text-[#8BA3BE]","children":"Rigid tiered pricing with limited flexibility"}]]}]]}]]}]}]
38:["$","h2","71",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"The 2026 SaaS Buyer's Checklist"}]
39:["$","p","73",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Based on the GTM transformation I've observed, here's a practical checklist for evaluating B2B SaaS vendors in 2026:"]}]
3a:["$","h3","75",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Before You Talk to Sales"}]
3b:["$","p","76",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Start a free trial and use the product for at least a week"]}]
3c:["$","p","77",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Check the vendor's community forum / knowledge base for relevance"]}]
3d:["$","p","78",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Read product reviews on G2, Capterra, and Reddit"]}]
3e:["$","p","79",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Identify your key integration requirements"]}]
3f:["$","p","80",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Estimate your total user count and likely annual spend"]}]
40:["$","h3","82",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"During the Sales Conversation"}]
41:["$","p","83",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Ask about implementation support: \"What does the first 30 days look like?\""]}]
42:["$","p","84",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Ask about pricing flexibility: \"Is your listed price negotiable at this ACV?\""]}]
43:["$","p","85",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Ask about escalation paths: \"If we have a critical issue, who do we contact?\""]}]
44:["$","p","86",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Ask about product roadmap: \"What are the top three features planned for this year?\""]}]
45:["$","p","87",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Ask about customer retention: \"What's your NRR and logo retention rate?\""]}]
46:["$","h3","89",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"After Signing"}]
47:["$","p","90",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Verify that your onboarding contact is the same person (or team) who sold you"]}]
48:["$","p","91",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Join the customer community or user group"]}]
49:["$","p","92",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Set up health checks at 30, 60, and 90 days"]}]
4a:["$","p","93",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["- [ ] Document your use case so the CS team can help you expand value"]}]
4b:["$","h2","95",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"Three Biggest Risks of the New GTM Model"}]
4c:["$","p","97",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["The leaner GTM org isn't all positive for buyers. Here are the risks to watch for:"]}]
4d:["$","h3","99",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Risk 1: Vanishing Post-Sale Support"}]
4e:["$","p","100",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["When reps handle the full cycle, they're less available for reactive support. The assumption is that most questions can be answered by documentation, community, or AI chatbots. If your organization requires hands-on support, ensure the vendor has a dedicated support tier or CSM allocation appropriate for your spend level."]}]
4f:["$","h3","102",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Risk 2: Price Increases from \"Land and Expand\" Pressure"}]
50:["$","p","103",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["With lower initial ACVs from self-serve, vendors are under pressure to expand accounts aggressively. Watch for: automatic seat upgrades, usage-based pricing that grows faster than your team, and aggressive cross-selling during support interactions. The best vendors make their expansion pricing transparent upfront."]}]
51:["$","h3","105",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-8 mb-3","children":"Risk 3: One-Size-Fits-All Feature Sets"}]
52:["$","p","106",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Flat GTM orgs that serve all customer segments through the same sales and support channels often result in products that satisfy average needs but excel at no specific use case. If your requirements are specialized, look for vendors with dedicated industry or vertical solutions, which typically require a higher-touch GTM approach."]}]
53:["$","h2","108",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"FAQ: B2B SaaS Buying in the New GTM Era"}]
54:["$","p","110",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: Should I still ask for a demo, or just start a trial?"}],""]}]
55:["$","p","111",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: Start a trial first. Come to the demo with specific questions. Sales teams in 2026 value informed buyers and will provide deeper, more useful answers."]}]
56:["$","p","113",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: How do I know if a vendor's self-serve tier is good enough?"}],""]}]
57:["$","p","114",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: Evaluate against your must-have requirements, not nice-to-haves. If you need custom compliance certifications, dedicated IP ranges, or white-labeled support, you'll likely need the enterprise tier."]}]
58:["$","p","116",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: Is usage-based pricing better than per-seat pricing?"}],""]}]
59:["$","p","117",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: It depends on your usage pattern. If your usage is steady and predictable, per-seat pricing offers cost certainty. If it's variable, usage-based can be more cost-effective but watch for minimum commitments."]}]
5a:["$","p","119",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: What questions should I ask in a discovery call that signal a vendor is aligned with my needs?"}],""]}]
5b:["$","p","120",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: Ask about their median customer size, their top three industries served, their NRR (net revenue retention) for your segment, and how they handle implementation for companies of your size."]}]
5c:["$","p","122",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Q: How important is community for evaluating a SaaS vendor?"}],""]}]
5d:["$","p","123",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["A: Very important. A vibrant community indicates product-market fit, responsive support, and long-term viability. Check the vendor's community for: active responses to questions, feature request acceptance rates, and user-led knowledge sharing."]}]
5e:["$","h2","125",{"className":"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#F0F4F8] mt-10 mb-4 tracking-tight","children":"The Bottom Line for B2B Software Buyers"}]
5f:["$","p","127",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["The 2026 B2B SaaS GTM transformation represents a fundamental rethinking of how software is sold and serviced. For buyers, the key takeaway is that ",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"you get the best results when you match your buying approach to the vendor's go-to-market model"}],"."]}]
60:["$","p","129",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Don't expect white-glove service from a self-serve-first vendor at a mid-market price point. Don't settle for a generic trial if you have enterprise requirements. And above all, recognize that the leaner vendor org means you need to be a more informed, proactive buyer."]}]
61:["$","p","131",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["The vendors that will thrive in this new environment are those that make it easy for informed buyers to evaluate, purchase, and succeed — without needing a salesperson to hold their hand through every step. Those are the vendors worth betting on."]}]
d:[["$","meta","0",{"charSet":"utf-8"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"viewport","content":"width=device-width, initial-scale=1"}]]
